&lt;h3&gt;Nikola installation&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nikola was installed following directions at https://getnikola.com/getting-started.html&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Updating the blog&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Load the blog source directory into vscode:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="code"&gt;&lt;pre class="code literal-block"&gt;# Navigate to the blog site repository directory
cd ~/Desktop/nikola-env/blog2025

# Activate virtual environment
source ../bin/activate

# Open directory in vscode
code .
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;Creating a new post&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Open a terminal and type &lt;code&gt;nikola new_post&lt;/code&gt;, then edit the new file in the &lt;code&gt;posts&lt;/code&gt; directory.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Deploying updates to GitHub pages&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Open a terminal and type &lt;code&gt;nikola github_deploy&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><category>blog</category><category>nikola</category><category>python</category><guid>https://aubreymoore.github.io/blog2025/posts/blog2025-technical-notes/</guid><pubDate>Wed, 16 Apr 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Welcome to Nikola</title><link>https://aubreymoore.github.io/blog2025/posts/welcome-to-nikola/</link><dc:creator>Roberto Alsina</dc:creator><description>&lt;figure&gt;
